<DOCNO>WT21-B26-35</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA086-000622-B031-340</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/heritage/library/categories/govern/cm11.html 204.71.237.88 19970209060504 text/html 30968
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
