<li>   Gregory B. Christiansen and Walter E. Williams, "Welfare Family Cohesiveness and Out of Wedlock Births," in Joseph Peden and Fred Glahe, <i>The American Family and the State</i> (San Francisco:  Pacific Institute for Public Policy Research, 1986), p. 398.
<li>    M. Anne Hill and June O'Neill, "Family Endowments and the Achievement of Young Children With Special Reference to the Underclass," <i>Journal of Human Resources</i>, Fall 1994, pp. 1090-1091.
